plus intuitives, plus,

00:01:30.590 --> 00:01:33.930 align:middle line:84%
plus, in order to
ground us in a much more

00:01:33.930 --> 00:01:37.410 align:middle line:84%
efficient way of understanding
our body-mind matrix.

00:01:37.410 --> 00:01:38.700 align:middle line:90%
>>JAIN: Absolutely.

00:01:38.700 --> 00:01:41.280 align:middle line:84%
